## LogicN: The Governed Tower Architecture

### Executive Summary

LogicN is a **High-Assurance Governance-as-Code** platform. Unlike traditional runtimes that rely on software-level policing, LogicN enforces security via **Deterministic Enforcement** and **Formal Proof**. By moving security from "runtime detection" to "compile-time proof and hardware-boundary gating," LogicN eliminates TOCTOU (Time-of-Check to Time-of-Use) vulnerabilities and creates an immutable, cryptographically verifiable audit trail.

